articles.author: Brian Murphy
articles.title: Barry Humphries, Australian comedian who created Dame Edna, dies at 89 - The Washington Post
articles.description: Dame Edna began as a satire and suburbia and became evolved into a global goddess of bling and irreverence that included a Tony Award.
